  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Help Provide Legal Support to Refugees in Greece</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">For over five years, ELIL has been running successful legal assistance programmes providing free, independent legal assistance to asylum seekers on Lesvos and Samos and in Athens. We are now seeking support to meet the increased need for legal assistance to Afghan refugees in Greece and to ensure that we are able to respond to a fast-changing context. Donations are tax deductible in the UK and US.</narrative>
  </description>
